SELECT CASE NVL(ESTADO,'ERROR') WHEN 'EJECUTANDO' THEN ESTADO||(1/0) WHEN 'OK' THEN CASE WHEN CURRENT_TIMESTAMP > (CASE PERIODICIDAD WHEN 'Y' THEN ADD_MONTHS(DATE_TRUNC('DAY',ULTIMA_CARGA), 12) /*YEAR, anual*/ WHEN 'M' THEN ADD_MONTHS(DATE_TRUNC('DAY',ULTIMA_CARGA), 1) /*MONTH, mensual*/ WHEN 'Q' THEN ADD_MONTHS(DATE_TRUNC('DAY',ULTIMA_CARGA), 3) /*QUARTER, trimestral*/ WHEN 'B' THEN DATE_TRUNC('DAY',ULTIMA_CARGA) + 14 /*WEEK, quincenal*/ WHEN 'W' THEN DATE_TRUNC('DAY',ULTIMA_CARGA) + 7 /*WEEK, semanal*/ WHEN 'D' THEN DATE_TRUNC('DAY',ULTIMA_CARGA) + 1 /*DAY, diario*/ WHEN 'H' THEN DATE_TRUNC('HOUR',ULTIMA_CARGA) + (1/24) /*HOUR, horario*/ WHEN '12H' THEN (ULTIMA_CARGA + (720/1440)) /* medios d铆as*/ WHEN 'N' THEN CURRENT_TIMESTAMP-1 ELSE ULTIMA_CARGA END) THEN NVL(TABLA,'') ||';'||NVL(PERIODICIDAD,'N') ||';'||NVL(RESPALDO,'N') ||';'||NVL(ESTADO,'ERROR') ||';'||TO_CHAR(NVL(ULTIMA_CARGA,TO_DATE('19000101','YYYYMMDD')),'YYYYMMDD') ||';'||NVL(RUTA_LOCAL_SQLUNLOAD,'') ||';'||NVL(FLAG_SISNOT_INICIO,'N') ||';'||NVL(FLAG_SISNOT_OK,'N') ||';'||NVL(FLAG_SISNOT_KO,'N') ||';'||NVL(FORMULA_FECHA_INICIAL,'TOTAL') ||';'||NVL(FORMULA_FECHA_FINAL,'TOTAL') ELSE 'NO CARGAR' END ELSE NVL(TABLA,'') ||';'||NVL(PERIODICIDAD,'N') ||';'||NVL(RESPALDO,'') ||';'||NVL(ESTADO,'ERROR') ||';'||TO_CHAR(NVL(ULTIMA_CARGA,TO_DATE('19000101','YYYYMMDD')),'YYYYMMDD') ||';'||NVL(RUTA_LOCAL_SQLUNLOAD,'') ||';'||NVL(FLAG_SISNOT_INICIO,'N') ||';'||NVL(FLAG_SISNOT_OK,'N') ||';'||NVL(FLAG_SISNOT_KO,'N') ||';'||NVL(FORMULA_FECHA_INICIAL,'TOTAL') ||';'||NVL(FORMULA_FECHA_FINAL,'TOTAL') END FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_GAI_CONTROL_CARGA") ?> WHERE 1=1 AND PAQUETE = '#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_PAQUETE'

UPDATE <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_GAI_CONTROL_CARGA") ?> SET ESTADO = 'EJECUTANDO', SESION = #GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_SESION, ULTIMA_EJECUCION = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, FECHA_INICIAL = (#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_FORMULA_FECHA_INICIAL), FECHA_FINAL = (#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_FORMULA_FECHA_FINAL), FORMULA_FECHA_INICIAL = NVL(FORMULA_FECHA_INICIAL, 'TOTAL'), FORMULA_FECHA_FINAL = NVL(FORMULA_FECHA_FINAL, 'TOTAL') WHERE 1 = 1 AND PAQUETE = '#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_PAQUETE' AND NVL(ESTADO,'ERROR') <> 'EJECUTANDO'

SELECT NZUTIL.ADMIN.REGEXP_REPLACE(NZUTIL.ADMIN.GROUP_CONCAT('@'||LPAD(ORDINAL_POSITION, 4, '0')||'@' ||COLUMNA, ','), '@[0-9]{4}@', '') AS GROUP_BY FROM (SELECT ORDINAL_POSITION, CASE WHEN ORDINAL_POSITION =1 THEN CASE WHEN TYPE_NAME <> 'VARCHAR' THEN 'CHR(34)||'||CHR(39)||A.COLUMN_NAME||CHR(39)||' '||A.COLUMN_NAME ELSE 'CHR(34)||'||CHR(39)||A.COLUMN_NAME||CHR(39)||' '||A.COLUMN_NAME END ELSE CASE WHEN ORDINAL_POSITION =( SELECT MAX(ORDINAL_POSITION) FROM DB_GAI_PRD.CONTROLES._v_odbc_columns1 WHERE 1=1 AND TABLE_NAME ='#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_TABLA') THEN CASE WHEN TYPE_NAME <> 'VARCHAR' THEN CHR(39)||A.COLUMN_NAME||CHR(39)||'||CHR(34)'||' '||A.COLUMN_NAME ELSE CHR(39)||A.COLUMN_NAME||CHR(39)||'||CHR(34)'||' '||A.COLUMN_NAME END ELSE CASE WHEN TYPE_NAME <> 'VARCHAR' THEN CHR(39)||A.COLUMN_NAME||CHR(39)||' '||A.COLUMN_NAME ELSE CHR(39)||A.COLUMN_NAME||CHR(39)||' '||A.COLUMN_NAME END END END AS COLUMNA FROM DB_GAI_PRD.CONTROLES._v_odbc_columns1 A WHERE 1=1 AND TABLE_NAME ='#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_TABLA') AS S;

SELECT NZUTIL.ADMIN.REGEXP_REPLACE(NZUTIL.ADMIN.GROUP_CONCAT('@'||LPAD(ORDINAL_POSITION, 4, '0')||'@' ||COLUMNA, ','), '@[0-9]{4}@', '') AS GROUP_BY FROM (SELECT ORDINAL_POSITION, CASE WHEN ORDINAL_POSITION =1 THEN CASE WHEN TYPE_NAME <> 'VARCHAR' THEN 'CHR(34)||NVL(CAST('||COLUMN_NAME||' AS VARCHAR(50)),'''')' ELSE 'CHR(34)||NVL('||COLUMN_NAME||','''')' END ELSE CASE WHEN ORDINAL_POSITION =( SELECT MAX(ORDINAL_POSITION) FROM DB_GAI_PRD.CONTROLES._v_odbc_columns1 WHERE 1=1 AND TABLE_NAME ='#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_TABLA' ) THEN CASE WHEN TYPE_NAME <> 'VARCHAR' THEN 'NVL(CAST('||COLUMN_NAME||' AS VARCHAR(50)),'''')||'||'CHR(34)' ELSE 'NVL('||COLUMN_NAME||','''')||'||'CHR(34)' END ELSE CASE WHEN TYPE_NAME <> 'VARCHAR' THEN 'NVL(CAST('||COLUMN_NAME||' AS VARCHAR(50)),'''')' ELSE 'NVL('||COLUMN_NAME||','''')' END END END AS COLUMNA FROM DB_GAI_PRD.CONTROLES._v_odbc_columns1 WHERE 1=1 AND TABLE_NAME ='#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_TABLA') AS S;

SELECT DISTINCT CAST(TBL_GAI_CONCILIACION.COD_CONCILIACION AS VARCHAR(80)) +';'+ISNULL(TBL_GAI_CONCILIACION.NOMBRE_CONCILIACION,'') +';'+ISNULL(TBL_GAI_CONCILIACION.TABLA_DESTINO,'') +';'+ISNULL(TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS.VALOR,'') +';'+ISNULL(TBL_GAI_CONCILIACION.USUARIO_ASIGNADO,'')+','+ ISNULL(TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS_OP.VALOR, '') FROM (((<?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_GAI_CONCILIACION") ?> INNER JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_GAI_WS_TRANSFORMACIONES") ?> ON TBL_GAI_CONCILIACION.COD_CONCILIACION = TBL_GAI_WS_TRANSFORMACIONES.COD_CONCILIACION) INNER JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_GAI_ESCENARIO") ?> ON TBL_GAI_ESCENARIO.COD_CONCILIACION = TBL_GAI_CONCILIACION.COD_CONCILIACION) LEFT JOIN <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS") ?> ON (TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS.COD_PADRE = TBL_GAI_ESCENARIO.COD_ESCENARIO AND TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS.PARAMETRO = 'V_RUTA_SQL_UNLOAD') LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT ISNULL(TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS.VALOR,'') VALOR FROM <?=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS") ?> WHERE TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS.PARAMETRO = 'V_CORREOS_OPERACIONES') TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS_OP ON 1=1 ) WHERE 1=1 AND TBL_GAI_WS_TRANSFORMACIONES.PAQUETE_WS = '#GLOBAL.V_0552_CTL_PAQUETE'
